This is from the our first session last night as Chris was asking if his 
technician helpers were around. It sounds like two way conversation to me, 
albeited limit here. I could hear some of this live, as some know, my 
hearing isn't the best. Chris's voice is muffled cuz #24 has a mic jack for 
the operator, and I neglected to have a mic to plug in, so the echo box mic 
was picking up Chris's voice.

Frank-S
